         <div type="translation">
            <ab>As[- - -];On the 25th: Anchorimphis [- - -]. (In the left margin:) Deceased(?).;Hera[- - -]: 4 drachmai;Hes[- - -]: 8 drachmai. (In the left margin:) Deceased(?).;Amm[- - -]: 2 drachmai.;Am - - - [- - -]: 8 drachmai. (In the left margin:) Deceased(?).;Kastor, son of Tamystha, of unknown father: 8 drachmai.;Sambas, his brother, (born) of the same mother: 8 drachmai.;Hosis, son of Harsutmis: . . drachmai . . obols.;Sarapion, son of Pisais, grandson of Horos: 8 drachmai.;Pisais, son of Horos, grandson of Ophellios: 8 drachmai.;Orseus, son of Harmiysis: 4 drachmai 4 obols.;Chairemon, son of Orsenouphis the elder: 4 drachmai 2 obols.;Heliodoros, son of Harphaesis: 4 drachmai 2 obols. (In the left margin:) Deceased(?).;On the 26th: Hosis, son of Orseus . . . : 4 drachmai.;Total: 440 drachmai 15 obols.;;(Traces of one more line, and of a second column)</ab>
